705065f-c.title: Brooklyn: Hunt's Alley - Henry Street
705065f-c.text:
(1)
Hhhint'sA0lkey, aorth side, east from Henry Street, showing rear of houses
on Remsen Street. In the background, is seen, from left to right, the
Montague Court Building, the qourt Remsen building and another building at

the Clinton Arms Hotel.
